          <hr>
          <!-- START 1st section -->
          <p>The amount of snow, rain, or water equivalent that accumulates during a time period will help forecasters determine the rate and magnitude of the load increase on the snowpack. In this document, Precipitation Rate refers to an estimate of the snow or rain rate. Precipitation Intensity is a measurement of water equivalent per hour.<\/p>
          <hr>
          <h3>Procedure<\/h3>
          
          <h3>Precipitation Type<\/h3>
          <p>Note the type of precipitation at the time of observation and record using the codes in <a href=\"#table1-2Accordion\">Table 1.2<\/a>.<\/p>
          <!-- START table 1-2 accordion -->
          <div class=\"accordion\" id=\"table1-2Accordion\">
          <div class=\"accordion-item\">
            <h2 class=\"accordion-header\" id=\"table1-2heading\">
            <button class=\"accordion-button collapsed text-info bg-light\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#table1-2collapse\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"table1-2collapse\">
              Table 1.2 Precipitation Type
            <\/button>
            <\/h2>
            <div id=\"table1-2collapse\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse collapse\" aria-labelledby=\"table1-2heading\" data-bs-parent=\"#table1-2Accordion\">
            <div class=\"accordion-body\">
              <!-- START table02 -->
              <div class=\"table-responsive\">
              <h5 id=\"table-1-2\">Table 1.2 Precipitation Type<\/h5>
              <table class=\"table table-bordered\">
              <thead class=\"thead-light\">
                <tr>
                <th scope=\"col\">Data Code<\/th>
                <th scope=\"col\">Description<\/th>
                <\/tr>
              <\/thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                <td>NO<\/td>
                <td>No Precipitation<\/td>
                <\/tr>
                <tr>
                <td>RA<\/td>
                <td>Rain<\/td>
                <\/tr>
                <tr>
                <td>SN<\/td>
                <td>Snow<\/td>
                <\/tr>
                <tr>
                <td>RS<\/td>
                <td>Mixed Rain and Snow<\/td>
                <\/tr>
                <tr>
                <td>GR<\/td>
                <td>Graupel and Hail<\/td>
                <\/tr>
                <tr>
                <td>ZR<\/td>
                <td>Freezing Rain<\/td>
                <\/tr>  
              <\/tbody>
              <\/table>
              <\/div>
              <!-- END table02 -->
            <\/div>
            <\/div>
          <\/div>
