          <!-- END table 1-2 accordion -->
          <h3>Precipitation Rate<\/h3>
          <p>Use the descriptors listed in <a href=\"#table1-3Accordion\">Table 1.3<\/a> to assess the precipitation rate at the time of observation. Record the estimated rate with the appropriate data code in <a href=\"#table1-3Accordion\">Table 1.3<\/a>.<\/p>
          <!-- START table 1-3 accordion -->
          <div class=\"accordion\" id=\"table1-3Accordion\">
          <div class=\"accordion-item\">
            <h2 class=\"accordion-header\" id=\"table1-3heading\">
            <button class=\"accordion-button collapsed text-info bg-light\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#table1-3collapse\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"table1-3collapse\">
              Table 1.3 Precipitation Rate
            <\/button>
            <\/h2>
            <div id=\"table1-3collapse\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse collapse\" aria-labelledby=\"table1-3heading\" data-bs-parent=\"#table1-3Accordion\">
            <div class=\"accordion-body\">
              <!-- START table03 -->
              <div class=\"table-responsive\">
              <h5 id=\"table-1-3\">Table 1.3 Precipitation Rate<\/h5>
              <table class=\"table table-bordered\">
              <thead class=\"thead-light\">
                <tr>
                <th scope=\"col\">Data Code<\/th>
                <th scope=\"col\">Description<\/th>
                <th scope=\"col\">Rate<\/th>
                <\/tr>
              <\/thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                <td colspan=\"3\"><strong>Snowfall Rate (this table provides examples; any appropriate rate may be specified)<\/strong><\/td>
                <\/tr>
                <tr>
                <td>S-1<\/td>
                <td>Very light snowfall<\/td>
                <td>Snow accumulates at a rate of a trace to about 0.5 cm (&Tilde; 0.25 in) per hour<\/td>
                <\/tr>
                <tr>
                <td>S1<\/td>
                <td>Light snowfall<\/td>
                <td>Snow accumulates at a rate of about 1 cm (&Tilde; 0.5 in) per hour<\/td>
                <\/tr>
                <tr>
                <td>S2<\/td>
                <td>Moderate snowfall<\/td>
                <td>Snow accumulates at a rate of about 2 cm (a little less than 1 in) per hour<\/td>
                <\/tr>
                 <tr>
                 <td>S5<\/td>
                 <td>Heavy snowfall<\/td>
                 <td>Snow accumulates at a rate of about 5 cm (&Tilde; 2 in) per hour<\/td>
                 <\/tr>
                <tr>
                <td>S10<\/td>
                  <td>Very heavy snowfall<\/td>
                  <td>Snow accumulates at a rate of about 10 cm (&Tilde; 4 in) per hour<\/td>
                <\/tr>
                <tr>
                  <td colspan=\"3\"><strong>Rainfall Rate<\/strong><\/td>
                <\/tr>
                <tr>
                <td>RV<\/td>
                  <td>Very light rain<\/td>
                  <td>Rain produces no accumulation, regardless of duration<\/td>
                <\/tr>
                <tr>
                  <td>RL<\/td>
                  <td>Light rain<\/td>
                  <td>Rain accumulates at a rate up to 2.5 mm (0.1 in) of water per hour<\/td>
                <\/tr>
                <tr>
                  <td>RM<\/td>
                  <td>Moderate rain<\/td>
                  <td>Rain accumulates at a rate between 2.6 to 7.5 mm (0.1 to 0.3 in) of water per hour<\/td>
                <\/tr>
                 <tr>
                   <td>RH<\/td>
                   <td>Heavy rain<\/td>
                   <td>Rain accumulates at a rate of 7.5 mm (0.3 in) of water per hour or more<\/td>
                 <\/tr>
                
                
              <\/tbody>
              <\/table>
              <\/div>
              <!-- END table03 -->
            <\/div>
            <\/div>
          <\/div>
